title: Udon Thani Rajabhat University Stadium
text: Udon Thani Rajabhat University Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Udon%20Thani%20Province">Udon Thani Province</a>, <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches.
